==爭議==
瑪莉娜·阿布拉莫維奇被指與崇拜撒旦的信仰有關<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2016/11/spirit-cooking-explained-satanic-ritual-or-fun-dinner.html |title=Report: Clinton Linked to Satanic Rituals Involving Kidnapped Children and Marina Abramovic |first=Eric |last=Levitz |journal=New York Magazine |language=en |access-date=2018-05-13 |archive-date=2018-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180811052020/http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2016/11/spirit-cooking-explained-satanic-ritual-or-fun-dinner.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>：報導指前美國國務卿[[希拉里|希拉里]]涉嫌參與一種名為「Spirit Cooking」的[[黑巫術|黑巫術]]儀式，而瑪莉娜·阿布拉莫維奇被指曾向其他人發邀請去參加這個儀式。而過往瑪莉娜·阿布拉莫維奇亦曾出版過一輯名為「Spirit Cooking with essential aphrodisiac recipes (complete portfolio), 1996」的作品<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.artnet.com/auctions/artists/marina-abramovic/spirit-cooking-with-essential-aphrodisiac-recipes-complete-portfolio |title=Marina Abramović: Spirit Cooking with essential aphrodisiac recipes (complete portfolio), 1996 |access-date=2018-05-13 |archive-date=2021-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323171854/https://www.artnet.com/auctions/artists/marina-abramovic/spirit-cooking-with-essential-aphrodisiac-recipes-complete-portfolio |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

但事實上，Spirit Cooking 只是把奇異的詩以豬血寫在牆上的古怪作品，不過是瑪莉娜眾多的表演與創作之一而已，而瑪莉娜自己在創作時事實上也參考了許多像是基督教、印度教、佛教、澳洲原住民等等，而這些並不代表瑪莉娜就是基督徒、佛教徒、薩滿，這個爭議只不過是政治上有意塑造，為了影響選情而毫無根據的陰謀論罷了。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Marina Abramovic’s Spirit Cooking|url=https://mitpress.mit.edu/blog/marina-abramovic%E2%80%99s-spirit-cooking|access-date=2022-04-04|date=2017-06-28|last=Press|first=The MIT|work=mitpress.mit.edu|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Some Believe Marina Abramovic Is the Ringleader of a Global Conspiracy. That's Ludicrous. But Here's What They Get Right|url=https://news.artnet.com/opinion/marina-abramovic-new-world-order-explainer-1838223|access-date=2022-04-04|date=2020-04-20|last=Davis|first=Ben|work=Artnet News|language=en-US}}</ref>

